descriptionHtml:
Are you Smart? If yes, please come to play Fill the Glass, A Brand New Water Puzzle Game, which is sure to make you happy! In this thrilling water-based physics game, you will start a difficult journey of fill the water in the glass to test if you are really smart! Your task is to draw a line with limited time to make a glass filled with water and bring a smile to the glass face.

Features :
- Dynamic mechanism. Draw lines freely to complete levels!
- Simple, smart and fun puzzles but can be challenging too
- Lots of levels with more coming soon!
- Fun and relaxing theme that will make you stay for quite some time

Try to find the best way to complete each level. You can come up with your own solution so be creative and don't be afraid to think outside the box!

Play Fill the Glass on your holidays and enjoy your time. Some levels may seem easy but let's see if you can actually get 3 stars.

You need to fill up a glass with water by tapping with perfect timing to release the water and make it flow all the way through to the cup to fill it and bring a smile again. Filling the glass with water can be very difficult, as you need to avoid obstacles, spikes, and more that could make the water spill out.
descriptionShort: Draw a line to make a glass filled with water to complete the puzzle game
